There are 3 observable trends for consideration from this data set:
- Males are the most profitable gender demographic (84.03% of all players), but they spend the least per person ($4.07/person/purchase).
- Players between the ages 20 and 24 are the largest age demographic (44.70% of all players), are the most profitable as a group, and spend more than most other age groups (with the exception of <10 and 35-39 year olds) per purchase.
- 71.88% of players are one time shoppers (they do not have more than one purchase).